<p>Using this Ruby on Rails project, build an MVP of a timesheet application.</p>

<p>Your submission should meet the following criteria:</p>
<ol>
  <li>A user should be able to click a "Clock In" button to begin tracking time.</li>
  <li>A user should be able to click a "Clock Out" button to stop tracking time.</li>
  <li>A user should see a list of all their time entries.</li>
  <li>A user should see be able to export all their clockin/clockout results in a single CSV.</li>
</ol>

<p>Some things to note:</p>
<ul>
  <li>A teacher will need to clock in and out multiple times a day (e.g., for lunch)</li>
